infoTooltip:
Connect to a new remote Docker daemon.
If only host and port are specified, an http connection will be enstablished.
If all fileds are filled, an HTTPS connection will be used instead.
For more informations, see the README.md
hostInfoTooltip:
Host name of the remote machine running the Docker daemon.
Can be an IP address.
portInfoTooltip: Port the Docker daemon will listen to. Defaults to 2375.
